# Agent Artifacts

- All working files go in `.agents/` -- never scatter files in the project root.
- Date-prefix files: `YYYY-MM-DD-description.md`.
- Write an ADR in `.agents/decisions/` for significant architectural choices.
- Clean up working files when they're incorporated or abandoned.
- `.agents/decisions/` is versioned (committed to git). Everything else in `.agents/` is gitignored.
